'The traps were only one of many defences Ashúrz Maufulug maintains, [placeholder]. The Orcs are also defended by several skilled archers.

'These archers patrol the outskirts of Ashúrz Maufulug for signs of approaching enemies. Defeat these archers, or we will be unable to attack the camp.

'When you have completed this task, return to me.'
'Very well done yet again, [placeholder]! However, there is still a great threat within Ashúrz Maufulug.'
'The archers of the Taughâsh are highly skilled. They are a threat that must be removed.'
'The archers of the Taughâsh are mighty. They are a threat that must be removed.'
The Orcs of Ashúrz Maufulug have placed many traps around their encampment, but those were only one of many defences.
Defeat Taughâsh archers at Ashúrz Maufulug ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Orc-archers can be found patrolling the outskirts of Ashúrz Maufulug, south and a little west from Echad Glamodúd.\n\nGlamodúd has asked you to defeat the Orc-archers who defend Ashúrz Maufulug.
Talk to Glamodúd at Echad Glamodúd
Glamodúd is at Echad Glamodúd, north and a little east from Ashúrz Maufulug.\n\nYou should return to Glamodúd with news of your victory.
